README.md
.SH DIAGNOSTICS 
Compile-time diagnostic and sanity checks can be enabled by setting TGL_ERROR_CHECK to 1 in the source code version of 
.I GL/gl.h 
as well as the system tinygl.h
.SH BUGS
Texture clipping is not functional.
